onMs":170883,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":3,"nextRunAtMs":1774314600000,"lastError":"Delivering to Feishu requires target <chatId|user:openId|chat:chatId>"}},{"id":"20ad25e9-a93b-4554-9c04-ac4c8f1f3016","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"飞书备份方案持续研究","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774139057733,"updatedAtMs":1774313554111,"schedule":{"expr":"15,45 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请研究飞书多维表格（Bitable）备份方案的可行性：\n\n## 研究任务\n\n1. **分析失败原因**\n   - 检查 feishu_bitable_create_app API 调用参数\n   - 尝试不同的参数组合（folder_token、name 等）\n   - 记录具体错误信息\n\n2. **替代方案探索**\n   - 方案 A：云文档 + 表格块（用 feishu_doc create_table）\n   - 方案 B：使用现有 Bitable（如果用户已有）\n   - 方案 C：云盘文件备份（JSON 原始数据）\n\n3. **实践测试**\n   - 尝试用 feishu_doc 在文档中创建表格\n   - 测试表格内容写入\n   - 验证是否可实现类似 Bitable 的结构化存储\n\n4. **输出报告**\n   - 哪种方案最可行？\n   - 需要什么额外权限？\n   - 推荐什么备份策略？\n\n## 记录要求\n\n写入文件：`memory/飞书备份研究日志.md`\n- 研究时间\n- 尝试的方法\n- 成功/失败\n- 下一步计划\n\n记住：目标是找到可靠的飞书备份方案，不一定要用 Bitable！"},"delivery":{"channel":"feishu","mode":"announce","to":"user:ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1"},"state":{"lastRunAtMs":1774313397007,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":157104,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":0,"nextRunAtMs":1774314900000}},{"id":"863f9a88-95b9-4f91-85d0-24c1e5a6d011","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:main","name":"牙齿再生深度思考","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774139144655,"updatedAtMs":1774314071831,"schedule":{"expr":"25,55 * * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"你是\"牙齿再生研究专家\"，专注于人类牙齿再生技术的前沿研究。\n\n## 本次思考任务（第 X 次）\n\n从以下方向选择一个深入思考（每次不同）：\n1. **干细胞再生** - 牙髓干细胞、间充质干细胞诱导牙胚形成\n2. **基因调控** - BMP、Wnt、Shh 信号通路激活牙齿发育基因\n3. **生物支架** - 3D 打印牙胚支架、生物材料引导再生\n4. **药物诱导** - USAG-1 抗体、小分子药物激活牙蕾\n5. **组织工程** - 体外培养牙胚 + 体内移植\n6. **神经血管重建** - 再生牙齿的神经和血液供应\n7. **免疫兼容** - 避免排斥反应\n8. **临床应用** - 从实验室到临床的转化路径\n\n## 输出格式\n\n```markdown\n## 🦷 牙齿再生研究 - 第 X 次思考\n**时间：** YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM\n**主题：** [具体方向]\n\n### 核心挑战\n[当前科学难题，200 字]\n\n### 前沿进展\n- [最新研究 1 + 引用]\n- [最新研究 2 + 引用]\n- [最新研究 3 + 引用]\n\n### 技术路径\n1. [方案 1 + 可行性分析]\n2. [方案 2 + 时间预测]\n\n### 关键突破点\n[最可能的突破方向 + 理由]\n\n### 时间预测\n- 实验室成功：X 年\n- 临床试验：X 年\n- 广泛应用：X 年\n\n---\n*持续思考中... 下次思考将聚焦 [下一个方向]*\n```\n\n## 记录要求\n\n1. **写入文件：** `memory/牙齿再生研究日志.md`\n2. **追加格式**，保留历史\n3. **每次 500-800 字**，深度分析\n4. **基于真实科学研究**，标注来源\n5. **发送到飞书**，让主人了解进展\n\n开始本次深度思考！"},"delivery":{"channel":"feishu","mode":"announce","to":"user:ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1"},"state":{"lastRunAtMs":1774313952831,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":119000,"lastDelivered":true,"lastDeliveryStatus":"delivered","consecutiveErrors":1,"nextRunAtMs":1774315500000,"lastError":"⚠️ ✉️ Message failed"}},{"id":"af6a6a57-8b20-481c-a0d9-de27076df635","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:body-repair-2026","name":"人体修复能力思考推送","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774060281695,"updatedAtMs":1774270030614,"schedule":{"expr":"0 10 * * *","kind":"cron","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"请研究并分享一个关于人类身体修复能力的前沿发现或有趣角度（如牙齿再生、器官自愈、细胞修复、组织工程等）。要求：1) 基于真实科学研究 2) 简短有趣 3) 包含一个令人惊叹的事实或进展。发送到微信：510723047。输出格式：【人体修复日报】+ 日期 + 主题 + 内容 + 来源/研究方向。"},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"user:ou_b317d2d01fed443d0a2e94a15f8a4ba1"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774317600000,"lastRunAtMs":1774240586625,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":26839,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":1,"lastError":"Channel is required when multiple channels are configured: feishu, openclaw-weixin Set delivery.channel explicitly or use a main session with a previous channel."}},{"id":"b5dcf669-096e-44ab-9631-bb70f9df28c1","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:body-repair-2026","name":"人体修复能力思考推送","enabled":true,"create